{"tid":1600162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"參與社區對話市民遭起底　政府譴責　私隱專員跟進","createTime":"2019-09-28T13:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T13:49:13.000Z","uid":51271,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"536f9353ec10739c530cbb5ae7b23dc62b6df14f","tid":1600162,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T13:29:06.000Z","msg":"政府表示，有參與星期四「社區對話」的市民，於網上遭公開個人資料，並受到滋擾和威嚇，發言人強烈譴責有關行為，並指個人資料私隱專員公署已在接獲投訴後，即時跟進和展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人表示，過去3個多月的社會爭議令香港陷入紛亂，政府希望與不同背景和立場的市民直接對話，通過和平、理性的溝通為香港尋找出路。<br />\n<br />\n發言人重申，香港是一個自由文明的社會，不同政見和立場的市民也享有言論、集會等自由，但任何人在行使這個權利時，都不應剝奪其他人的自由，更不應使其他人受到傷害。任何人不論立場，都不應因言論而受到欺凌、威嚇，只有互相尊重不同意見，求同存異，香港才能踏上「復和之路」。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 篤航班人比人起底你又唔出聲？"},{"pid":"8cb55cf731b48f8b10a654477e41144d22c15c38","tid":1600162,"uid":124410,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T13:37:43.000Z","msg":"驚就唔好去對話會啦"},{"pid":"d4afa9a5c1d4aa2111da3d398f4ada47324604df","tid":1600162,"uid":25635,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"即係起岩左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4544a4df844af6275ee57afd3e1c70b2e42830d","tid":1600162,"uid":308588,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T13:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9uVvTug.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9uVvTug.png&h=9f4ca6f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"98a4cae1de2c50fdb6857de0c07c60b26426ae87","tid":1600162,"uid":121504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a4544a4df844af6275ee57afd3e1c70b2e42830d","tid":1600162,"uid":308588,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T13:39:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9uVvTug.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9uVvTug.png&h=9f4ca6f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T13:4